data.description: Welcome to 749 Golden Spring Drive! This charming house is now available for sale, offering a wonderful opportunity for you to create your dream home. With its prime location and desirable features, this property is sure to capture your attention.  Step inside and be greeted by an inviting open floor plan that allows for seamless flow and abundant natural light throughout. The first-floor living area provides convenience and comfort, making it the perfect space for relaxation or entertaining guests.  A laundry room on the main floor is an added convenience.  This house boasts three spacious bedrooms, providing ample space for your family or guests. The primary bath is roomy with a large walk-in closet.  Additionally, this property includes a two-car parking space, ensuring that you'll never have to worry about finding parking. The unfinished basement with 9 ft ceilings presents endless possibilities for customization, allowing you to transform it into the perfect space to suit your needs.  Situated in Cold Spring Estates, this house is close to all amenities. Whether you're in search of shopping centers, restaurants, or recreational facilities, everything you need is just a short distance away.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your own. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and see firsthand the potential this property has to offer. We look forward to helping you find your ideal home at 749 Golden Spring Drive.
